./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6278:- Close-read MN 22, the Heart Sutra, Mandukya Upanishad, Dogen's Genjokoan, and Tannisho for explicit custody markers: who or what may authorize insight after the method reaches its threshold?
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6305:- Practitioner-method source: Dogen's practice-realization in Bendowa, via local prior work and Bielefeldt's Dogen's Manuals of Zen Meditation, used as a lens for testing truth through enacted practice. Critique of the lens: it can make source history look secondary even when community, lineage, and harm require source accountability.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6369:Survived critique from comparison theory, the Chandogya and SN 22.59 carrier conflict, Dogen's practice-realization pressure, social-connection grounding, and checking-risk cautions by narrowing the claim into two distinct gates.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6442:- Result: Preliminary search found strong overlap with Smith, Freiberger, Panikkar, Wuthnow, Dogen scholarship, and OCD checking literature. Novelty should stay moderate and depend on the two-gate operational distinction.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6518:- Dogen practice-realization, used analogically for learning truth through enacted practice rather than pre-certification.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6556:- Run an originality audit against comparative method, pastoral discernment, seeker spirituality, Dogen practice-realization, therapeutic anti-checking models, and social connection interventions.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6573:Some teachings say there is no distance to cross, but this does not mean there is no care to keep. The error is to hear no path as no support. A no-distance teaching removes the private project of becoming spiritual; it should not remove correction, companionship, schedule, duty, teacher, text, vow, or ordinary accountability. The frontier should therefore be narrowed: before asking what remains after self-negation, ask whether the path gives the practitioner ownership of the process at all. If it does not, the important question becomes where correction is held when ownership is refused. This matters now because exhausted people often turn relief into another project, while isolated people can turn private insight into a room no one else can enter.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6585:- Primary-text comparison: Dogen's Bendowa refuses a separation between cultivation and realization while still recommending direct practice, https://afe.easia.columbia.edu/ps/japan/dogen.pdf. Huangbo's On the Transmission of Mind refuses seeking as a way to grasp mind, consulted via Blofeld PDF record, https://merton.bellarmine.edu/s/merton/media/51897, and Chan transmission analysis, https://www.mdpi.com/2077-1444/12/4/279. Shinran's Tannisho denies self-powered practice while preserving teacher, vow, and correction against divergence, https://jodoshinshu.faith/tannisho-a-record-in-lament-of-divergences/.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6586:- Thinking method source: Dogen's practice-realization was used as a lens to stop assuming before, after, method, and result. Critique of that lens: it can dissolve real sequence too quickly, so it was checked against Shinran's warnings about calculation and Huangbo's sharper refusal of seeking.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6593:Huangbo may weaken the model from inside it. His search-refusal can be read as refusing not only private ownership but also every mediating support the analyst wants to name. Calling his discourse a support may domesticate a teaching meant to cut support-seeking itself. Dogen also strains the model because practice-realization may not relocate support at all; practice may simply be the expression, not a holder of continuity. A further weakness is circularity: coders may find support wherever a tradition has teachers, texts, or communities, which would make the model descriptive rather than predictive. The claim should be weakened if no-distance practitioners flourish without identifiable correction supports, or if their failures do not cluster around privatization, passivity, or performance.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6621:Tags: critique-mode, no-distance, support, burnout, loneliness, achievement-pressure, self-negation
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6649:Survives the anomaly that Dogen, Huangbo, and Shinran each refuse a simple method-then-result timeline, yet each still preserves some form of practice, discourse, vow, teacher, or warning against distortion.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6723:- Next action: Search extended cognition, ritual studies, Pure Land studies, Dogen studies, Chan studies, Dzogchen studies, and mindfulness critique for this exact scope condition.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6733:- Next action: Code Bendowa, Uji, Huangbo, Tannisho, selected Dzogchen manuals, and practitioner reports for ownership refusal, correction holder, and named failure mode.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6758:- If this model is right, then Dogen-style, Huangbo-style, Shin-style, and Dzogchen-style texts should refuse private ownership while still protecting some concrete source of correction. If they deny both ownership and corrigible support, the model is weakened.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6762:- Protocol improvement: Dogen's lens should remain a warning against false sequence, not a universal solvent. Pair it with a method that preserves concrete responsibility, such as early Buddhist not-mine analysis or Shinran's warning against self-power calculation.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6792:This may be speech-act theory and constructivist religious-studies caution in local clothing. It may also overcorrect: a tradition can mean exactly what it says, not merely use words pedagogically. An Advaita commentator may show that self-luminosity is direct disclosure rather than a speech role, and a Buddhist commentator may show that not-self instruction is also doctrine, not only a training device. The strongest anomaly is any direct-recognition lineage where the words are treated as immediate recognition and not as instruction, warning, or inference. Dogen-style practice-realization and Other Power also strain the model because word, act, gift, and realization may not separate cleanly. If blind coders cannot reliably distinguish sentence roles, or if commentaries contain explicit inference rules that make role-coding unnecessary, the model should be weakened or merged into prior verification work.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:6927:- Prediction: Blind coders should classify sentence role before doctrinal conclusion in Brihadaranyaka 3.7.23, SN 22.59, SN 22.95, Heart Sutra negation passages, and Dogen practice-realization texts. If role codes are unreliable or do not change later conclusion coding, the model is weakened.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:7051:The closest prior arguments already cover much of the ground: dreamless-sleep report debates, Advaita and Buddhist comparisons, not-self as strategy, Lumenary's report-grammar and correction-holder records. The remaining distinction is narrower: post-gap report grammar and residue policy should not be treated as the first audit layer. The first layer is whether silence is being asked to serve as evidence without enough return discipline. This reframes the frontier from 'which clause after the gap counts as evidence' to 'which supports keep the person from turning the gap into a verdict.' Novelty is therefore modest, but the narrowing may prevent overclaim and improve practice safety.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:7277:The model may over-psychologize comparison. Some words are protected less by private self-checking than by living institutions, teachers, ritual forms, and community correction. Zen, Chan, Pure Land, Dzogchen, and Mahamudra can also treat words, gestures, trust, and recognition as inseparable from practice, which may make a receiver-wound sheet feel like an outsider's grid. The model is weakened if dual-trained practitioners can translate contested terms without naming receiver wounds and still show clearer conduct, less misuse, and better care than people using the added check.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:7695:This is not highly novel. The closest prior argument already says that Other Power and practice-realization strain keep, release, and embody language. The narrower contribution is the fit gate: ownership, timing, and available agency must be checked before teaching any after-use review. Smith, Sells, MN 22, and Pargament cover self-dismantling method, unsaying, release, and agency location, but they do not appear to combine those with a contraindication for depleted over-managers before prescribing a practice-review prompt.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:7702:- Primary-text comparison: MN 22 validates proper use and later release; the Heart Sutra denies attainment while still relying on Prajnaparamita; Dogen practice-realization denies a later verification outside practice; Shinran and Tannisho deny practitioner-owned merit in Other Power.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:7768:Survived pressure from MN 22's proper-use-and-release pattern, the Heart Sutra's no-attainment-with-practice hybrid, Dogen practice-realization, Shinran Other Power, and near-neighbor scholarship on self-dismantling method, unsaying, and agency location. It survives only as a scoped correction, not as a universal doctrine.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:7843:- Next action: Search upaya scholarship, Dogen practice-realization scholarship, Jodo Shinshu scholarship, spiritual direction ethics, rumination literature, and metacognitive therapy for close versions of the fit gate.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:7850:- Prediction: If ownership and after are real scope conditions, Tannisho, Shinran's jinen honi writings, and Dogen's Bendowa should refuse or relocate the question of what the practitioner keeps, releases, or embodies after the method works. If they use clear practitioner-owned keep, release, or embody language, the model is weakened.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:7888:- If this model is right, then texts that deny practitioner ownership or a discrete after should resist clean coding on keep, release, and embody axes. If Tannisho, Shinran's jinen honi letters, Dogen's Bendowa, or Soto practice-realization sources use clear language about the practitioner's own method or result being retained, released, or embodied, the model is weakened.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:8351:This may psychologize traditions that do not frame their speech as repair. Pure Land nembutsu, Dzogchen pointing-out, sacramental speech, and communal prayer may work as entrustment, recognition, vow, or participation rather than as a remedy for a named modern wound. The model also risks making every teaching pass through modern therapeutic usefulness, which could flatten worship, metaphysics, ritual duty, and liberation claims. It weakens sharply if trained practitioners say the repair field adds no decision value beyond ordinary source criticism, teacher guidance, or spiritual-bypass screening.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:8677:Before asking what remains after self-negation, ask what question made the distance appear. Some paths teach a real crossing: effort is needed, the old pattern is released, and the person can later say a task was done. Some paths refuse the crossing question: practice is already the living of what it seeks, trust is not self-made, or seeking itself is the distortion. When a student carries a crossing question into a no-distance teaching, the teaching can become another private project: prove the insight, manage the result, defend the state, or withdraw from correction. The first check is not what remains; it is which question the teaching allows. For people exhausted by self-improvement and performance, this matters because a liberating sentence can become one more scoreboard if the wrong question is left in charge.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:8685:- Mode: Critique. Active frontier: Remainder pressure after self-negation. This record narrows broad remainder and continuity maps by adding a pre-remainder question check, and by lowering novelty because local near-duplicates already exist.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:8686:- What is held now: before coding what remains after self-negation, code the question the teaching allows the practitioner to ask, such as crossing, receiving, enacting, repairing, or refusing ownership.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:8688:- Primary text comparison: Shinran's reply to Senshin says there is no calculation on the practicer and names Other Power as no working true working, so it refuses the self-owned question; https://shinranworks.com/letters/a-collection-of-letters-zensho-text/what-we-call-other-power/.
./runs/20260530-151348-claude-generate-an-original-lumenary-doctrine-building-/prompt.md:8689:- Primary text comparison: Dogen's Bendowa and the local Dogen Uji source card pressure any before-and-after reading because practice and verification are treated as one act, not a later result to manage; https://afe.easia.columbia.edu/ps/japan/dogen.pdf and notes/source-cards/buddhism-dogen-uji.md.
